title: Fair Foods - Expense Dashboard - with Dash
description: This project is a dynamic and interactive web application built using **Dash** - **Plotly** - and **Pandas** to visualize and analyze monthly expenses. The dashboard allows users to explore expenses by category view trends over time and analyze their spending patterns with various types of visualizations.
